{"tid":28217,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"multiplier multiplicand which comes first？","createTime":"2016-12-07T20:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T20:33:02.000Z","uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa2a42466470ede77d1aa2a41472f317f9d9d05","tid":28217,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T20:26:40.000Z","msg":"呢兩日同人討論緊呢個問題（其實係爭論）<br />\n亦希望帶起叫做學術少少嘅討論所以喺LIHKG開POST問吓<br />\n<br />\n對方支持3 x 5同5 x 3係冇錯，我同佢解釋過multiplier同multiplicand嘅區別同關係，但係佢指出就算係咁都唔代表擺位有一個『通俗』嘅規定，亦即係第一個擺multiplicand都好，擺multiplier都好，數學上教育上都係冇一個規定。<br />\n<br />\n所以我搵咗呢個source畀佢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crewtonramoneshouseofmath.com/multiplicand-and-multiplier.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crewtonramoneshouseofmath.com%2Fmultiplicand-and-multiplier.html&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=8e7d482e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.crewtonramoneshouseofmath.com/multiplicand-and-multiplier.html</a><br />\n尾六段係主點<br />\n<br />\n我亦有見過外國小學生嘅功課因為multiplier同multiplicand擺錯咗而畀老師打交叉，坦白講我唔係為啖氣要拗贏乜，我淨係想知到底數學上係點睇呢件事。"},{"pid":"f3239167b2d3f22cf839a64fe0d992c9671bec40","tid":28217,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T20:27:27.000Z","msg":"屌我係咪開撚咗去吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fa1da5561ea22156aa527c04ee89a502dbe6d8","tid":28217,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T20:29:54.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得教育上係應該要規定個擺位，從而令學生一眼就分得清邊個係multiplier同multiplicand，呢個習慣可以當做鞏固concept"},{"pid":"d7c8dd4cd29f148867289533311327ee33752871","tid":28217,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T20:30:53.000Z","msg":"有冇讀數撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550a8cddfce65e08e670fe3781b12131fbe96e64","tid":28217,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T20:33:02.000Z","msg":"屌去學術台再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}